title: Test Preso - Houston housing market
text:
This slide shows the annual houses sold in Houston, TX from the year 2000-2015.

library(tidyverse)
txhousing |> filter(city=="Houston") |> 
             group_by(year) |> 
             summarize(sales=sum(sales)) |> 
             ggplot(aes(x=year, y=sales)) + 
                geom_line() + 
                ggtitle("Annual Houses Sold in Houston, TX")
